Use the standard library
This is how to max_fill of grid and capacity:
  Remember that total is 0
  Remember that i is 0
  Do this grid's length times:
    Remember that row is item i in grid
    Remember that j is 0
    Remember that row_sum is 0
    Do this row's length times:
      Remember that row_sum is sum of row_sum and item j in row
      Increase j by 1
    End do
    Remember that total is sum of total and quotient of row_sum and capacity
    When remainder of row_sum and capacity is not 0, then:
      Increase total by 1
    End when
    Increase i by 1
  End do
  The answer is total
Now you know